Package: opensearch-dashboards-desktop
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libnotify4, libnss3, libxss1, libxtst6, xdg-utils, libatspi2.0-0, libsecret-1-0
Maintainer: OpenSearch Contributors <opensearch@amazon.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/opensearch-project/dashboards-desktop
Description: Agent-first desktop app for OpenSearch and Elasticsearch
 A local-first, privacy-respecting alternative to cloud AI chat tools
 that doubles as a unified OpenSearch and Elasticsearch admin tool.
 Supports local models (Ollama), cloud models (OpenAI, Anthropic, Bedrock),
 MCP servers, plugins, and skills.
